//Osseous lesion

Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 09 of Cardiac MRI
When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then Finding dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Osseous lesion' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled

And 'Humerus' radio button is enabled
And 'Clavicle' radio button is enabled
And 'Sternum' radio button is enabled
And 'Ribs' radio button is enabled
And 'Vertebral body' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Humerus' radio button
Then 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled
And 'Size' input field is enabled

And 'Benign' radio button is enabled
And 'Malignant' radio button is enabled
And 'Unknown' radio button is enabled
When I select 'Benign' radio button
Then 'Hemangioma' radio button is enabled
And 'Paraspinal cyst' radio button is enabled
And 'Enostosis' radio button is enabled



When I select 'Clavicle' radio button
Then 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled
And 'Size' input field is enabled

And 'Benign' radio button is enabled
And 'Malignant' radio button is enabled
And 'Unknown' radio button is enabled
When I select 'Benign' radio button
Then 'Hemangioma' radio button is enabled
And 'Paraspinal cyst' radio button is enabled
And 'Enostosis' radio button is enabled



